(9, 'Signatura Digital', '<div class="portlet-borderless-container" style="">\n	<div class="portlet-body">\n		<div class="journal-content-article">\n			<div class="contingut">\n				<div class="titul">\n					<h3>\n						<span style="color:#008080;">Tr&agrave;mits i gestions amb certificat digital: certificats reconeguts a la UAB</span></h3>\n				</div>\n				<p>\n					Un certificat digital &eacute;s l&#39;equivalent electr&ograve;nic d&#39;un document d&#39;identitat i s&#39;acostuma a utilitzar per:</p>\n				<ul>\n					<li>\n						Autenticar la vostra identitat, per exemple, per fer un tr&agrave;mit en l&iacute;nia.</li>\n					<li>\n						Signar digitalment un document o un correu electr&ograve;nics.</li>\n				</ul>\n				<p>\n					&nbsp;</p>\n				<p>\n					A la UAB es poden fer&nbsp;els tr&agrave;mits telem&agrave;tics amb els&nbsp;certificats digitals que es detallen a continuaci&oacute;.</p>\n				<p>\n					Els tr&agrave;mits d&#39;aquesta seu que requereixen d&#39;un certificat digital estan identificats amb l&#39;etiqueta</p>\n				<p>\n					<a href="https://seuelectronica.uab.cat/certificats-reconeguts" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="https://seuelectronica.uab.cat/documents/10548/85961/clau/6a8806c1-1fc2-477e-b1cb-dbe633884c26?t=1436440909045" style="width: 30px; height: 30px;" /></a>&nbsp; <span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong><span style="background-color: rgb(41, 124, 105);">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Tr&agrave;mit amb certificat digital &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong></span></span></p>\n				<p>\n					&nbsp;</p>\n				<p>\n					Si no es disposa d&#39;un d&#39;aquests certificats, es pot fer la sol&middot;licitud als enlla&ccedil;os seg&uuml;ents.</p>\n				<ul>\n					<li>\n						<a href="https://seuelectronica.uab.cat/certificat-idcat" target="_blank">Certificat idCAT</a></li>\n					<li>\n						<a href="https://seuelectronica.uab.cat/usuaris-i-sol-licituds-t-cat" target="_blank">Certificat T-CAT</a></li>\n					<li>\n						<a href="https://seuelectronica.uab.cat/com-es-fa-servir-dni-e" target="_blank">DNI electr&ograve;nic</a></li>\n					<li>\n						<a href="https://seuelectronica.uab.cat/com-es-fa-servir-fnmt" target="_blank">Certificat de l&#39;FNMT</a></li>\n				</ul>\n				<p>\n					Si teniu un d&#39;aquests certificats, es pot comprovar la validesa en qualsevol dels enlla&ccedil;os seg&uuml;ents:</p>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n</div>\n<div class="portlet-boundary portlet-boundary_56_ portlet-static portlet-static-end portlet-borderless portlet-journal-content " id="p_p_id_56_INSTANCE_WbReOzRhuuGD_">\n	<div class="portlet-borderless-container" style="">\n		<div class="portlet-body">\n			<div class="journal-content-article">\n				<div class="links top10">\n					<ul>\n						<li>\n							<a href="https://www.eacat.cat/web/guest/signatura" target="_blank">Validador del Consorci AOC</a></li>\n						<li>\n							<a href="https://valide.redsara.es/valide/" target="_blank">VALIDE, Servei de Validaci&oacute; del Ministeri d&#39;Hisenda i d&#39;Administracions P&uacute;bliques</a></li>\n					</ul>\n				</div>\n			</div>\n			<div class="entry-links">\n				&nbsp;</div>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n</div>\n<div class="portlet-boundary portlet-boundary_56_ portlet-static portlet-static-end portlet-borderless portlet-journal-content " id="p_p_id_56_INSTANCE_2ihyv026yvfu_">\n	<div class="portlet-borderless-container" style="">\n		<div class="portlet-body">\n			<div class="journal-content-article">\n				<div class="links top10">\n					<h3 class="verd">\n						<span style="color:#008080;">Sobre els tr&agrave;mits del registre electr&ograve;nic amb certificat digital</span></h3>\n					<ul>\n						<li>\n							<a href="https://seuelectronica.uab.cat/requisits-tecnics">Requisits t&egrave;cnics</a></li>\n						<li>\n							<a href="https://seuelectronica.uab.cat/certificats-reconeguts">Tr&agrave;mits i gestions amb certificat digital</a></li>\n						<li>\n							<a href="https://seuelectronica.uab.cat/documents-annexos">Documents annexos</a></li>\n						<li>\n							<a href="https://seuelectronica.uab.cat/terminis-de-tramitacio">Terminis de tramitaci&oacute;</a></li>\n						<li>\n							<a href="https://seuelectronica.uab.cat/dies-inhabils">Dies inh&agrave;bils</a></li>\n						<li>\n							<a href="https://seuelectronica.uab.cat/data-i-hora-oficials">Data i hora oficials</a></li>\n						<li>\n							<a href="https://seuelectronica.uab.cat/preguntes-frequents-sobre-tramits">Preguntes freq&uuml;ents sobre aquest tr&agrave;mit</a></li>\n					</ul>\n				</div>\n			</div>\n			<div class="entry-links">\n				&nbsp;</div>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n</div>\n<div class="portlet-column portlet-column-last span2" id="column-3">\n	<div class="portlet-dropzone portlet-column-content portlet-column-content-last" id="layout-column_column-3">\n		<div class="portlet-boundary portlet-boundary_56_ portlet-static portlet-static-end portlet-borderless portlet-journal-content " id="p_p_id_56_INSTANCE_E5zT8xD9Ca0s_">\n			<div class="portlet-borderless-container" style="">\n				<div class="portlet-body">\n					<div class="journal-content-article">\n						<div class="links top10">\n							<h3 class="verd">\n								<span style="color:#008080;">Com identificar-se</span></h3>\n							<ul>\n								<li>\n									<a href="https://seuelectronica.uab.cat/certificats-reconeguts">Tr&agrave;mits i gestions amb certificat digital</a></li>\n								<li>\n									<a href="https://seuelectronica.uab.cat/tramits-i-gestions-amb-niu-i-contrasenya">Tr&agrave;mits i gestions amb NIU i contrasenya</a></li>\n								<li>\n									<a href="https://seuelectronica.uab.cat/tramits-sense-identificacio-digital">Tr&agrave;mits i gestions presencials sense identificaci&oacute; digital</a></li>\n							</ul>\n						</div>\n					</div>\n				</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n		<div class="portlet-boundary portlet-boundary_56_ portlet-static portlet-static-end portlet-borderless portlet-journal-content " id="p_p_id_56_INSTANCE_dxwgcCEpmyhe_">\n			<div class="portlet-borderless-container" style="">\n				<div class="portlet-body">\n					<div class="journal-content-article">\n						<aside class="bloc-info">\n						<h3 style="text-align: justify;">\n							<span style="color:#008080;">Pots descarregar-te el manual de Signatura Electr&ograve;nica amb el certificat IDCAT, que &eacute;s la signatura digital que s&#39;utilitza a la UAB.</span></h3>\n						<p class="mesinfo">\n							<a href="http://doctoratcirurgia.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/Manual Signatura Electrònica.docx" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="/DocsCKeditor/images/document.png" style="width: 30px; margin: 15px; float: left; text-align: justify; height: 32px;" /></a></p>\n						<p class="mesinfo">\n							&nbsp;</p>\n						<p class="mesinfo">\n							<a href="http://doctoratcirurgia.uab.cat/DocsCKeditor/files/Manual%20Signatura%20Electr%C3%B2nica.docx" target="_blank">Manual de Signatura Electr&ograve;nica</a></p>\n						<div class="entry-links">\n							&nbsp;</div>\n						<h4>\n							<a href="https://seuelectronica.uab.cat/certificats-reconeguts" target="_BLANK"> I</a><a href="https://seuelectronica.uab.cat/certificats-reconeguts" target="_BLANK">nformaci&oacute; sobre certificaci&oacute; i notificaci&oacute; electr&ograve;niques </a></h4>\n						<p>\n							<b>Oficina de Gesti&oacute; de la Informaci&oacute; i la Documentaci&oacute; (OGID)</b><br />\n							Tel. 93 581 2752<br />\n							<a href="mailto:certificacio.digital@uab.cat">certificacio.digital@uab.cat</a></p>\n						<p class="mesinfo">\n							&nbsp;</p>\n						</aside></div>\n				</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', 1, 7, 0),
