(78, 'Frequently asked questions', '<h4>\n	1- Who has to do the annual monitoring?</h4>\n<p>\n	All of the PhD students, except the students that deposit their thesis in the actual academic course.</p>\n<h4>\n	2- What documentation do I have to send?</h4>\n<p>\n	All Phd student must always bring the summary report in the maximum date of delivery.</p>\n<h4>\n	3- Are there any documents that I must send?</h4>\n<p>\n	Yes, the hospital sessions attendance certificate (1st activity) or the individual report of an article sent to a scientific journal (2nd activity) according in the monitoring you are enrolled.</p>\n<h4>\n	4- Who has to send the hospital sessions attendance certificate (1st activity)?</h4>\n<p>\n	All PhD students that are enrolled in First year monitoring (69501).</p>\n<h4>\n	5- Who has to send the individual report of an article sent to a scientific journal (2nd activity)?</h4>\n<p>\n	All PhD students that are enrolled in Second year monitoring (69502) and subsequent monitoring years (69503, etc.).</p>\n', 106, '', 4, 2),
