(279, NULL, '<p>\n	<img alt="" src="/DocsCKeditor/images/índex.jpg" style="width: 150px; height: 94px; float: left; margin: 5px 10px;" /></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	Us informem que el per&iacute;ode de matr&iacute;cula del curs 2017/18 estar&agrave; obert fins al <span style="color:#008080;"><strong>15 de desembre de 2017</strong></span> mitjan&ccedil;ant l&#39;<a href="http://sia.uab.es/servei/ALU_AUMDOC_PORT_CAT.html" target="_blank">aplicatiu d&#39;Automatr&iacute;cula</a>.</p>\n<p>\n	A l&#39;apartat <a href="http://sia.uab.es/cgi-bin/gpwd/gestio_pwd.html?&amp;idioma=ca&amp;pais=ES" target="_blank">Gesti&oacute; de paraules de pas</a> del web http://sia.uab.es podeu generar-vos l&#39;usuari i la contrasenya.</p>\n<p>\n	Si trobeu algun problema per generar aquestes dades, aquells que es trobin en un hospital universitari de la UAB, podeu apropar-vos a la Unitat Docent de la Facultat de Medicina de la UAB que teniu al vostre hospital, o podeu contactar amb el correu <a href="mailto:ed.matricula@uab.cat">ed.matricula@uab.cat</a>.</p>\n<p>\n	Per a qualsevol incid&egrave;ncia en el proc&eacute;s de matr&iacute;cula, podeu trucar al tel&egrave;fon de l&#39;automatr&iacute;cula: <strong><span style="color:#008080;">93 581 38 36</span></strong>.</p>\n<p>\n	Tamb&eacute; podeu formalitzar la matr&iacute;cula a l&#39;Escola de Doctorat. Per aquest tr&agrave;mit haureu de sol&middot;licitar <a href="http://cita.uab.cat/escola-doctorat/escola-doctorat/index.php?lang=ca" target="_blank">cita pr&egrave;via</a>.</p>\n<p>\n	El procediment per a formalitzar la matr&iacute;cula (preus i modalitats de pagament) est&agrave; publicat en aquest <a href="http://www.uab.cat/web/estudiar/doctorat/matricula/matricula-resta-de-cursos-1345664829320.html" target="_blank">enlla&ccedil;</a>.</p>\n', 'Matrícula online del curs acadèmic 2017/18', '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00', '2017-10-01', '', 1, NULL, 0),
(280, NULL, '<p>\n	<img alt="" src="/DocsCKeditor/images/índex.jpg" style="width: 150px; height: 94px; float: left; margin: 5px 10px;" /></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	We inform you that registration for the academic course 2017-18 will be open until <strong><span style="color:#008080;">15th December 2017</span></strong> through <a href="https://web1.uab.es:31504/cosmos/Controlador/?@ebf2f349580da806=@1bedd0984ff1624c&amp;@57b88e10f1a90c1a=@a039d9c04653ef8c&amp;@d2e9d205e120747b=@218720ae9af7baf62a3dd8305aa3900108dfb8e3d53d460e&amp;@f159383c5f17f705a3a0887a97288719=@61349e75b9612652&amp;@516cbd36a6c7b80e=@e76b8f5339ba2321&amp;@b86ba36b9abde0a9=@acc80a2f900b7223&amp;@7768acd4afb2a0dcaab9840b9661a38391fdaa47be8ebfbb=@f6313b39283a9692&amp;@1542a058212e2087=@fcedbb18de37e7eb&amp;@d9ce157cc24bed8c=@b1359d06a0218df1" target="_blank">PhD online enrolment</a>.</p>\n<p>\n	If you do not remember your user (NIU) and password you can visit <a href="http://sia.uab.es/cgi-bin/gpwd/gestio_pwd.html?&amp;idioma=en&amp;pais=GB" target="_blank">Password management</a>.</p>\n<p>\n	If you encounter any problem obtaining your NIU and password and you work in a UAB university hospital, you can go to the UAB Teaching Unit in the hospital or you can write an email to <a href="mailto:ed.matricula@uab.cat">ed.matricula@uab.cat</a>.</p>\n<p>\n	For any problem you have during the process of enrolment call the PhD online enrolment phone <strong><span style="color:#008080;">93 581 38 36.</span></strong></p>\n<p>\n	If you want to register personally you need to make an <a href="http://cita.uab.cat/escola-doctorat/escola-doctorat/index.php?lang=en" target="_blank">appointment</a> at the School for Doctoral Studies.</p>\n<p>\n	The procedure of enrolment (payment and prices) is published in this <a href="http://www.uab.cat/web/study-abroad/phds/enrolment/registration-subsequent-years-1345691784257.html" target="_blank">link</a>.</p>\n', 'PhD online enrolment for academic course 2017/18', '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00', '2017-10-01', '', 1, NULL, 2),
(281, NULL, '<p>\n	&nbsp;<br />\n	<span style="color:#008080;"><strong>Admis<img alt="" src="/DocsCKeditor/images/37729479_s.jpg" style="width: 125px; height: 125px; float: left; margin-left: 5px; margin-right: 5px;" />sion</strong></span> to the PhD in Surgery and Morphological Sciences for the <strong><span style="color:#008080;">academic course 2018-19</span></strong> is opened until <strong>16th November 2018</strong>&nbsp;using the <a href="https://web1.uab.es:31501/Navegacion/InicioAlSeALWqSO.html?&amp;@1542a058212e2087=@fcedbb18de37e7eb&amp;@d9ce157cc24bed8c=@b1359d06a0218df1&amp;@495523f567d311df=@50453a3d12bf797b#" target="_blank">online application</a>.</p>\n<p>\n	Before beginning your application make sure you satisfy the <a href="index.php#!/Access requirements_939_1" target="_blank">admission requirements</a>, have all the <a href="index.php#!/Admission_940_1" target="_blank">necessary documents</a> which you will need to scan and have seen the <a href="http://www.uab.cat/web/postgraduate/phds/all-phd-programmes/admission/admission-application/surgery-and-morphological-sciences-1345467765272.html?param2=1345657891083" target="_blank">admissions calendar</a>.</p>\n<p>\n	For more information about the procedure and the steps to follow, go to section <a href="index.php#!/Admission_940_1" target="_blank">Admission</a> in our website and section <a href="http://www.uab.cat/web/study-abroad/phds/admission/admission-new-doctoral-studies-regulated-by-rd-99/2011-1345666996343.html" target="_blank">Admission</a> in the web of the School of Doctoral Studies.<br />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', 'Admission to the PhD 2018-19', '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00', '2018-04-04', '', 1, 1, 2),
(282, NULL, '<p>\n	<img alt="" src="/DocsCKeditor/images/ddd_logo_150x129.gif" style="width: 100px; height: 86px; float: left; margin: 5px;" />The Library of the Medicine Faculty of UAB has prepared a direct search to look for doctoral theses read in our PhD programme in DDD <em>(Dip&ograve;sit Digital de Documents de la UAB)</em>.</p>\n<p>\n	Click <a href="https://ddd.uab.cat/search?ln=en&amp;p=Departament+de+Cirurgia&amp;c=tesis&amp;f=author+" target="_blank">here</a> to go to the search.<br />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', 'Consult our doctoral theses in DDD', '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00', '2017-10-01', '', 0, 2, 2),
(283, NULL, '<p>\n	<img alt="" src="/DocsCKeditor/images/information-1027300_640.jpg" style="width: 80px; height: 80px; float: left; margin: 5px;" />Consult last financial aids and grands for researchers and PhD students.</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n	For more information click <a href="http://www.uab.cat/web/-1282904340935.html?language=en&amp;param3=tipusEstudi&amp;param4=ESTDO" target="_blank">here</a>.<br />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', 'Financial aids and grands', '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00', '2017-10-01', '', 0, 5, 2),
(284, NULL, '<p>\n	<img alt="" src="/DocsCKeditor/images/5.JPG" style="width: 150px; height: 84px; margin: 5px; float: left;" /><strong><span style="color:#008080;">Support for writing PhD theses in Catalan or English, 2017</span></strong></p>\n<p>\n	The objective of this support is to provide occasional language support given by a language teacher to those who are writing a doctoral thesis in Catalan or English at the Universitat Aut&ograve;noma de Barcelona, to contribute to the overall linguistic quality of the final text. There are two types of support:</p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		Support for writing a doctoral thesis in <span style="color:#008080;"><strong>Catalan.</strong></span></li>\n	<li>\n		Support for writing a doctoral thesis in <span style="color:#008080;"><strong>English.</strong></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	Under no circumstances the tutorials will involve the correction of the thesis. The period for submitting applications is from the date of publication of the call for applications to <span style="color:#008080;"><strong>1 December, 2017.</strong></span></p>\n<p>\n	For more information, click <a href="http://www.uab.cat/web/listado-becas-sin-left-menu/detall-de-l-ajut-1284986965563.html?language=en&amp;param1=1345721196427&amp;param2=UAB-FATWIRE&amp;tq=idiomes" target="_blank">here</a>.<br />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', 'Support for writing PhD theses', '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00', '2017-10-01', '', 0, 5, 2),
